title: mc chris is resurrected - a fan made remix cd
description:
This is a fan made remix of "mc chris is dead." mc made every track available as an a capella so I got to work. Here&#039;s the track list

01 older crowd every1 nose
02 pizza tutte
03 kill it roy world
04 roller coaster like ohh
05 onstar from my moma
06 falynn upbeat
07 freaks stronger
08 reese i decided
09 ninja master grindin
10 nrrd grrl tore up
11 never give up keep goin
12 mc is gold
13 bonus - beetlejuice
14 bonus - screamin w/ Idle Warship
15 bonus - m & Z rough cut

I threw in some bonus cuts that I did not do, just rare little gems I don&#039;t see ever getting released.


all mp3 files with 320 kbps except the last three which are 192 kbps and 
ones 96 kbps.
